[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1684","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1684.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1018","title":"Linux Kernel IPChains IP 分片绕过安全漏洞","description":"Linux 内核 2.2.10 及更早版本中的 IPChains 防火墙组件在处理 IP 分片数据包时存在分片重组缺陷，在检查包头前未正确重组 IP 分片，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送多个偏移量为 0 的精心构造的 IP 分片，绕过防火墙过滤规则实现对内部网络的未授权访问。该漏洞影响 Linux 2.2.10 及之前版本内核，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1018"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-27T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:31.960","remediation":"升级至 Linux 内核 2.2.11 及以上版本（该版本已修复 IP 分片重组检查问题），或迁移至 2.4.x/2.6.x 等后续长期支持内核系列。若无法升级内核，可在防火墙规则中添加 `-f` 参数丢弃分片包作为临时缓解：`iptables -A INPUT -f -j DROP`。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93312523904591&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/543","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19301","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1018.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1018","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1018.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1018.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1018.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3xc5-vgfg-rqw3/GHSA-3xc5-vgfg-rqw3.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/543/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1018.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1684.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0406","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0406.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0710","title":"Squid cachemgr.cgi 未授权连接漏洞","description":"Squid 代理服务器在安装时将 cachemgr.cgi 管理脚本放置在公开 Web 目录下，导致远程攻击者无需认证即可直接访问该脚本，并利用其作为中转代理连接到任意内部或外部系统，造成信息泄露与未授权资源访问。该漏洞影响 Red Hat Linux 5.2/6.0 及包含 Squid 2.2 之前版本的其他发行版，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0710"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-25T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:53.680","remediation":"立即从 Apache CGI 目录（如 /var/www/cgi-bin/）中移除 cachemgr.cgi 脚本，或通过 Apache 配置添加访问控制（Order deny,allow; Deny from all）仅允许受信 IP 访问。同时安装 Red Hat RHSA-1999-025 或 Debian DSA-576 提供的 Squid 安全更新包，升级至修复版本。如无法立即打补丁，可在 cachemgr.cgi 所在目录创建 .htaccess 文件添加 HTTP 基本认证作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://fedoranews.org/updates/FEDORA--.shtml","http://www.debian.org/security/2004/dsa-576","http://www.redhat.com/archives/fedora-announce-list/2005-May/msg00025.html","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/RHSA-1999-025.html","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/RHSA-2005-489.html","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/archives/rh52-errata-general.html#squid","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/2059","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2385","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20465"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0406.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0406.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0406.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0014","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0014.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0224","title":"Microsoft Windows NT Messenger Service 长用户名拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 Messenger 服务在解析超长用户名时存在边界处理缺陷，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可向目标系统发送特制的超长用户名数据包，触发服务崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞利用方式简单，攻击者无需复杂工具即可通过标准网络协议发包实施攻击，影响 Windows NT 4.0 全版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0224"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-07-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:56.923","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 针对 Windows NT 4.0 的 Service Pack 5 (SP5) 或更高版本，该补丁修复了 Messenger Service 对畸形用户名处理不当的问题。对于已停止支持的旧系统，建议升级至 Windows Server 2003 或更高版本；若无法升级，可在服务管理器中禁用 \"Messenger\" 服务以消除攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0224","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/329","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-0224.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0224.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0224","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0224.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0224.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0224.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0014.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0994","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0994.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1165","title":"GNU fingerd 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"GNU fingerd 1.37 存在权限处理不当漏洞，程序在访问用户信息前未能正确放弃特权，导致本地攻击者可通过两种方式利用：一是在 .fingerrc 文件中放置恶意程序获取 root 权限；二是利用 .plan、.forward 或 .project 文件的符号链接读取系统任意文件。该漏洞影响 GNU fingerd 1.37 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高，需手动修复或禁用 finger 服务。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1165"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:51.533","remediation":"建议立即升级 GNU fingerd 至 1.37 以上版本，该版本已修复权限提升漏洞。更推荐的方案是直接禁用 finger 服务（systemctl disable fingerd 或在 inetd/xinetd 配置中注释 finger 行），因为该服务在现代网络环境中已无必要且存在安全隐患。如必须使用，应限制 .plan/.forward/.project 等文件的写权限，禁止普通用户在这些文件中使用符号链接，并删除 .fingerrc 文件的可执行权限以防止恶意程序执行。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93268249021561&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/2478","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/535"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0994.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0808","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0808.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0810","title":"Samba nmbd 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Samba 2.0.5 的 NetBIOS 名称服务守护进程（nmbd）存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标发送特制的 NetBIOS 名称服务请求数据包，导致 nmbd 进程崩溃或进入死循环，从而停止响应正常的名称解析请求，造成网络服务中断。该漏洞影响 Samba 2.0.5 及之前版本，攻击复杂度低，无需用户交互。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0810"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:06.230","remediation":"升级 Samba 至 2.0.5 或更高版本（推荐 2.0.6），该版本修复了 nmbd 处理异常 NetBIOS 名称时陷入死循环或崩溃的问题。如无法立即升级，可在防火墙层面过滤 UDP 137 端口的入站 NetBIOS 名称服务请求作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0810"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0808.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0575","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0575.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0811","title":"Samba smbd 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Samba 2.0.5 之前版本的 smbd 守护进程在处理畸形消息命令时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可向目标 Samba 服务发送特制的恶意消息包触发该漏洞，导致服务进程崩溃或实现本地权限提升，获取系统高权限。该漏洞影响所有 Samba 2.0.5 之前版本，CVSS 评分为 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0811"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:06.360","remediation":"升级 Samba 至 2.0.5 或更高版本，该版本修复了 smbd 进程处理畸形消息命令时的缓冲区溢出漏洞。如无法升级，可在 smb.conf 中限制可访问 smbd 的源 IP 地址范围作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/536","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19428"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0575.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0408","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0408.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0721","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0/2000 Local Security Authority Subsystem LSA Request 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 及 Windows 2000 的本地安全机构子系统（LSA）存在输入验证漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的畸形 LSA 请求，导致 LSA 服务崩溃，造成系统拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 和 Windows 2000 等版本，无需身份认证即可远程触发，危害等级高。Microsoft 官方已发布安全更新修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0721"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-20T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:55.073","remediation":"安装 Microsoft Security Bulletin MS99-021 提供的安全更新补丁，或升级至 Windows 2000 Service Pack 1 及以上版本。如无法升级，可在防火墙层面过滤发往 LSA 服务的异常 TCP/UDP 流量作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ231457","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-049.shtml","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-020"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0408.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1683","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1683.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1011","title":"Microsoft Data Access Components (MDAC) RDS 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Microsoft Data Access Components (MDAC) 中的远程数据服务 (RDS) DataFactory 组件暴露了不安全的内部方法，远程攻击者可通过 IIS 发送特制的 HTTP 请求，利用该组件绕过安全限制直接执行任意系统命令。该漏洞影响 IIS 3.0/4.0、MDAC 2.1 等组件，攻击无需身份认证，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。微软已发布安全公告及补丁修复此漏洞。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1011"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:31.110","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-025 提供的补丁，或升级至 Windows 2000 及以上版本（默认禁用 RDS DataFactory）。如无法升级，删除注册表键 `HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Services\\W3SVC\\Parameters\\ADCLaunch\\RDSServer.DataFactory` 以禁用该危险组件，同时在 IIS 管理器中移除 `/msadc/` 虚拟目录映射。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-054.shtml","http://www.osvdb.org/272","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-004","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-025","https://www.securityfocus.com/bid/529","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19424","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1011.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1011","https://github.com/fankh/vulnerability-poc/blob/e4734a5d374932e0e8adfb714d6049181237b752/1999/CVE-1999-1011/README.md","https://github.com/e-m-b-a/emba/blob/968abdc74763b43a3cdd216fbb1950cab484f982/config/msf_cve-db.txt","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1011.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1011.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1011.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qcm7-2qvw-4c58/GHSA-qcm7-2qvw-4c58.json","https://github.com/decal/werdlists/blob/81edb463f7f6311c85defefaf75ac9cd58e5cfb9/exploit-info/symantec-attack-signatures.txt","https://github.com/Chudry/Xerror/blob/07ec57cabcd27cdb47c89af452bdf4ed07207347/xerror/parsing/msf_module_result/msf_module_cve.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1683.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1683.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1683.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0306","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0306.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0692","title":"Cray Unicos Array Services 守护进程默认认证绕过漏洞","description":"Cray UNICOS 操作系统中的 Array Services 守护进程（arrayd）存在默认配置不当漏洞。该服务在默认安装情况下关闭了身份认证机制，导致远程攻击者无需任何凭证即可直接连接 arrayd 端口，并以 root 权限在目标系统上执行任意命令。攻击条件极低——只需目标开放 arrayd 服务且使用默认配置即可完成利用。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，影响 Cray UNICOS 系列操作系统。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0692"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-07-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:51.550","remediation":"升级 Cray Unicos 至厂商修复版本（如 8.0 及以上补丁级别），或修改 arrayd 配置文件启用认证（设置 require_authentication=yes）。如无法升级，使用 iptables 限制仅有信任管理节点可访问 arrayd 端口（默认 TCP/1050）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-052.shtml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0692.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0692","https://github.com/fankh/vulnerability-poc/blob/479b29734109e75b43136719820cebdc00fad096/1999/CVE-1999-0692/README.md","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0692.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0692.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-g2hc-xmvw-hhph/GHSA-g2hc-xmvw-hhph.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0692.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--9e4ef6a4-48d0-4517-8dd9-a548963a1dd4.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0306.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1700","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1700.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1086","title":"Novell NetWare IPX 管理会话伪骗权限提升漏洞","description":"Novell NetWare 5及更早版本在IPX协议上运行且数据包签名级别低于3时存在安全漏洞。远程攻击者可通过伪造IPC分片数据包中的MAC地址来欺骗NetWare核心协议(NCP)调用，从而在未经授权的情况下获取管理员权限。该漏洞危害严重，CVSS评分10.0，可导致目标系统完全受控。建议升级数据包签名级别至3或以上以进行防护。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1086"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-15T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:41.520","remediation":"将 NetWare 服务器 NCF 文件中 `SET PACKET SIGNATURE LEVEL` 设置为 3 或更高，强制要求 IPX 数据包签名验证，防止 MAC 地址欺骗攻击。如无法调整签名级别，可考虑禁用 IPX 协议并迁移至 TCP/IP 网络，或使用 VLAN 隔离限制攻击来源。建议升级至 Novell 6 及以上版本以获得完整修复。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93214475111651&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/528","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1086.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1086","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1086.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1086.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1086.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qhf9-4cg8-h46m/GHSA-qhf9-4cg8-h46m.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1086.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000696.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1700.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0995","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0995.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1166","title":"Linux Kernel 2.0.37 Segment Limit 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Linux Kernel 2.0.37 版本中对于自定义段限制（Segment Limit）的编码处理存在缺陷，导致本地攻击者能够通过访问并修改内核内存来提升权限至 root。该漏洞源于内核未正确验证段限长值，使得低权限用户可利用特定系统调用绕过内存访问限制。攻击者需拥有本地系统账户并具备代码执行能力，成功利用后可完全控制目标系统。该漏洞影响 Linux Kernel 2.0.37 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1166"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:51.663","remediation":"建议立即升级 Linux 内核至 2.0.38 或更高版本（如 2.2.x 系列），该漏洞在内核 2.0.38 中已修复。若无法升级，可通过限制本地用户对 /dev/mem 和 /dev/kmem 的访问权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/18156","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/523","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19419"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0995.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0574","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0574.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0809","title":"Netscape Communicator Cookie 安全策略绕过漏洞","description":"Netscape Communicator 4.x 版本存在安全绕过漏洞。当用户启用 JavaScript 且已选择\"仅接受来自正浏览页面同一服务器之 Cookie\"选项时，浏览器仍不会对 Cookie 设置行为发出警告。攻击者可利用恶意网页绕过 Cookie 同源策略，跨站设置或窃取用户 Cookie，导致用户隐私泄露或会话劫持。漏洞影响 Netscape Communicator 4.x 全系版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0809"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:06.117","remediation":"停止使用 Netscape Communicator 4.x，升级至 Mozilla Firefox 或其它现代浏览器，并在浏览器设置中禁用 JavaScript 作为临时缓解措施。对于仍必须使用 Netscape 的场景，可在浏览器首选项中关闭 JavaScript 功能（Edit → Preferences → Advanced → Scripts & Plugins → 取消启用 JavaScript）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0809"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0574.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0509","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0509.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0728","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 键盘鼠标 IOCTL 权限许可与访问控制漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统存在权限控制缺陷，本地用户可直接调用控制键盘和鼠标的 IOCTL 设备控制指令，无需管理员权限即可禁用输入设备。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 等版本，攻击者需具备本地登录权限，成功利用后可导致系统输入功能失效，属于本地权限滥用型漏洞。CVSS 评分 7.8，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0728"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:55.960","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-024 提供的补丁程序，该补丁已在 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 5 及后续版本中集成。对于仍在运行 Windows NT 4.0 的系统，应立即升级到受支持的操作系统版本（如 Windows Server 2016/2019/2022）。临时缓解措施：限制非授权用户对服务器的交互式登录权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ236359","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-024"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0509.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0453","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0453.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0752","title":"Netscape Enterprise Server SSL Handshake 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Netscape Enterprise Server 的 SSL 握手处理过程中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标服务器发送特制的 SSL 握手请求触发该溢出，导致服务进程崩溃从而引发拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Netscape Enterprise Server 3.6 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0752"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:58.993","remediation":"建议将 Netscape Enterprise Server 升级至 4.0 或更高版本以修复 SSL 握手缓冲区溢出漏洞。由于该产品已停止维护，长期方案应迁移至仍在支持的 Web 服务器（如 Apache HTTP Server 或 Nginx）。临时缓解措施可在网络层限制异常 SSL 握手请求频率。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0752","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19416"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0453.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1306","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1306.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0918","title":"Microsoft Windows IGMP 报文处理拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows 95/98/NT 3.51/NT 4.0/2000 的 IGMP 协议实现存在输入验证缺陷（CWE-20），远程攻击者可向目标系统发送特制的分片 IGMP 数据包，触发协议栈解析异常，导致目标系统蓝屏崩溃或服务完全停止。该漏洞无需用户交互即可远程触发，影响所有受支持的 Windows 9x/NT 系列版本，攻击者只需发送少量畸形数据包即可造成拒绝服务。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0918"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:19.657","remediation":"Windows 95/98 用户请通过 Microsoft Windows Update 安装安全更新或下载 MS99-034 补丁（KB Q238329）；Windows NT 4.0 用户请安装 Service Pack 6a 及后续安全汇总。上述系统均已终止支持，建议升级至 Windows 10/11 或 Windows Server 2016 以上版本。临时缓解措施：在边界防火墙上禁用 IGMP 协议或过滤碎片化 IGMP 报文。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ238329","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/514","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-034","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19415"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1306.toml"}]